---
---
<section class="spotlight-section">
  <!-- ── BLOQUE A: Xacobitos ── -->
  <div class="spotlight-row" id="spotlight-a">
    <div class="spotlight-text">
      <span class="sp-label">Xacobitos</span>
      <h2 class="sp-title">Colecciona criaturas<br />de la mitología gallega</h2>
      <p class="sp-body">
        Meigandras, trasgos, mouros y más de 50 criaturas únicas aguardan a lo
        largo del Camino. Cada criatura tiene su historia, sus poderes y su
        rareza. ¿Serás capaz de completar el bestiario?
      </p>
      <ul class="sp-bullets">
        <li>✦ Más de 50 criaturas coleccionables</li>
        <li>✦ Aparecen según tu ubicación y la hora del día</li>
        <li>✦ Raridades: común, rara, épica y legendaria</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="spotlight-mockup" aria-label="Mockup de la pantalla Xacobitos">
      <div class="phone-mockup" style="transform: rotate(3deg);">
        <div class="phone-notch" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="phone-screen">
          <!-- Header -->
          <div class="mock-header">
            <span class="mock-title-sm">Xacobitos</span>
            <span class="mock-badge-pill">8/15</span>
          </div>
          <!-- Featured creature -->
          <div class="mock-creature-card">
            <div class="creature-icon" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6b21a8, #9333ea);">🌿</div>
            <div class="creature-info">
              <div class="creature-name">MEIGANDRA</div>
              <div class="creature-rarity">✦ Rara</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Progress -->
          <div class="mock-progress-wrap">
            <div class="mock-progress-label">
              <span>Pasos hoy</span>
              <span class="mock-progress-val">2.500 / 5.000</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mock-progress-track">
              <div class="progress-bar-fill mock-progress-bar" data-fill="50%" style="width:0%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Grid -->
          <div class="mock-grid">
            <div class="mock-grid-item collected">🦎 <span>Trasgo</span></div>
            <div class="mock-grid-item collected">🌊 <span>Moura</span></div>
            <div class="mock-grid-item locked">❓ <span>???</span></div>
            <div class="mock-grid-item locked">❓ <span>???</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sp-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- ── BLOQUE B: Mochila ── -->
  <div class="spotlight-row reversed" id="spotlight-b">
    <div class="spotlight-mockup" aria-label="Mockup del diario de peregrino">
      <div class="phone-mockup" style="transform: rotate(-3deg);">
        <div class="phone-notch" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="phone-screen">
          <div class="mock-header">
            <span class="mock-title-sm">Mi Mochila</span>
            <span class="mock-badge-pill">Día 1</span>
          </div>
          <!-- Diary entry -->
          <div class="diary-entry">
            <div class="diary-photo" aria-hidden="true">
              <div class="diary-photo-inner">🏔️</div>
            </div>
            <p class="diary-text">
              "Hoy conocí a una peregrino brasileña en el refugio. El paisaje de la meseta me dejó sin palabras..."
            </p>
            <div class="diary-emotions">
              <span class="emotion-tag">😊 Feliz</span>
              <span class="emotion-tag">💪 Motivado</span>
              <span class="emotion-tag">🙏 Agradecido</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Stamps -->
          <div class="mock-stamps-row">
            <div class="stamp-circle" style="background: rgba(255,225,0,0.9); border: 2px solid #ffe100;">
              <span>⛪</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stamp-circle" style="background: rgba(45,122,69,0.4); border: 2px solid rgba(45,122,69,0.7);">
              <span>🌄</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stamp-circle" style="background: rgba(59,130,246,0.3); border: 2px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.5);">
              <span>🍃</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stamp-add">+</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="spotlight-text">
      <span class="sp-label">Mochila</span>
      <h2 class="sp-title">Tu diario de peregrino<br />en el bolsillo</h2>
      <p class="sp-body">
        Cada día del Camino merece ser recordado. La Mochila es tu espacio
        personal para guardar fotos, pensamientos y emociones de cada etapa.
        Colecciona sellos digitales en cada punto importante del recorrido.
      </p>
      <ul class="sp-bullets">
        <li>✦ Diario multimedia con fotos y texto</li>
        <li>✦ Registro de emociones diarias</li>
        <li>✦ Sellos digitales en hitos del Camino</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sp-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- ── BLOQUE C: Social ── -->
  <div class="spotlight-row" id="spotlight-c">
    <div class="spotlight-text">
      <span class="sp-label">Social Peregrino</span>
      <h2 class="sp-title">Comparte el Camino<br />con el mundo</h2>
      <p class="sp-body">
        El Camino une a personas de todo el planeta. Con Santi a GO! puedes
        seguir el progreso de otros peregrinos, compartir tus hazañas y
        celebrar juntos cada etapa completada.
      </p>
      <ul class="sp-bullets">
        <li>✦ Feed en tiempo real de la comunidad</li>
        <li>✦ Rankings y logros compartidos</li>
        <li>✦ Retos y misiones grupales</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="spotlight-mockup" aria-label="Mockup de la pantalla social">
      <div class="phone-mockup" style="transform: rotate(2deg);">
        <div class="phone-notch" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="phone-screen">
          <div class="mock-header">
            <span class="mock-title-sm">Comunidad</span>
            <span class="mock-badge-pill">🔴 En vivo</span>
          </div>
          <!-- Stats -->
          <div class="mock-stats-row">
            <div class="mock-stat">
              <div class="stat-val">23.5</div>
              <div class="stat-unit">km hoy</div>
            </div>
            <div class="mock-stat-divider"></div>
            <div class="mock-stat">
              <div class="stat-val">4:56</div>
              <div class="stat-unit">tiempo total</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Progress bar -->
          <div class="mock-progress-wrap" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
            <div class="mock-progress-label">
              <span>Etapa 5 · Pamplona → Logroño</span>
              <span class="mock-progress-val">68%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mock-progress-track">
              <div class="progress-bar-fill mock-progress-bar" data-fill="68%" style="width:0%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Community posts -->
          <div class="mock-posts">
            <div class="mock-post">
              <div class="post-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a5c35, #ffe100);">M</div>
              <div class="post-content">
                <div class="post-name">María 🇧🇷</div>
                <div class="post-text">¡Terminé la meseta! 🎉 Día más duro pero el más bonito</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mock-post">
              <div class="post-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6b21a8, #2d7a45);">K</div>
              <div class="post-content">
                <div class="post-name">Klaus 🇩🇪</div>
                <div class="post-text">Capturé a la Meigandra épica 🌿 ¡La criatura más rara!</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .spotlight-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a2516 0%, #071910 100%);
    padding: 100px 28px;
  }
  .spotlight-row {
    max-width: 1160px;
    margin: 0 auto 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 72px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .spotlight-row.reversed .spotlight-text { order: 2; }
  .spotlight-row.reversed .spotlight-mockup { order: 1; }

  .sp-divider {
    max-width: 1160px;
    margin: 80px auto;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 225, 0, 0.2), transparent);
  }

  .sp-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 3.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #ffe100;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .sp-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(30px, 3.5vw, 44px);
    line-height: 1.08;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .sp-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .sp-bullets {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .sp-bullets li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    padding-left: 4px;
  }

  /* Phone Mockup */
  .spotlight-mockup {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    will-change: transform;
  }
  .phone-mockup {
    width: 220px;
    border-radius: 36px;
    background: #111;
    border: 3px solid #2a2a2a;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 500ms ease, box-shadow 500ms ease;
  }
  .phone-mockup:hover {
    transform: scale(1.04) rotate(-1deg) !important;
    box-shadow: 0 40px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,225,0,0.15);
  }
  .phone-notch {
    width: 80px;
    height: 20px;
    background: #111;
    border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .phone-screen {
    padding: 8px 14px 20px;
    background: #151515;
    min-height: 380px;
  }
  .mock-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  }
  .mock-title-sm {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .mock-badge-pill {
    background: rgba(255, 225, 0, 0.15);
    color: #ffe100;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,225,0,0.3);
  }
  /* Xacobitos mockup */
  .mock-creature-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }
  .creature-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 22px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .creature-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .creature-rarity {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #ffe100;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .mock-progress-wrap {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .mock-progress-label {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .mock-progress-val { color: #ffe100; font-weight: 700; }
  .mock-progress-track {
    height: 6px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .mock-progress-bar {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffe100, #ffc800);
    border-radius: 3px;
    transition: width 0s;
  }
  .mock-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .mock-grid-item {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  .mock-grid-item span {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  }
  .mock-grid-item.collected { border-color: rgba(255,225,0,0.25); }
  .mock-grid-item.locked { opacity: 0.4; }

  /* Mochila mockup */
  .diary-entry {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .diary-photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 70px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a5c35, #0f3d26);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .diary-photo-inner { font-size: 32px; }
  .diary-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .diary-emotions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 5px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .emotion-tag {
    background: rgba(255,225,0,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,225,0,0.2);
    color: #ffe100;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 3px 7px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  .mock-stamps-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 8px 0;
  }
  .stamp-circle {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px;
  }
  .stamp-add {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  }

  /* Social mockup */
  .mock-stats-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 12px 0;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  }
  .mock-stat { text-align: center; }
  .stat-val {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #ffe100;
  }
  .stat-unit {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 9px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .mock-stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 32px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  }
  .mock-posts { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .mock-post {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .post-avatar {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .post-name {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffe100;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .post-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .spotlight-row { gap: 40px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .spotlight-section { padding: 72px 20px; }
    .spotlight-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .spotlight-row.reversed .spotlight-text { order: 1; }
    .spotlight-row.reversed .spotlight-mockup { order: 2; }
    .phone-mockup { transform: none !important; }
    .sp-divider { margin: 48px auto; }
  }
</style>
